# Rate Limiter APi Service

Per-Client rate limiting service using sliding window algo

## APIs
1. Register Client -- Post /clients
2. Check Rate Limit -- Get /allow/{clientId}

## Run
mvn spring-boot:run

## Docker
docker build -t rate-limiter
docker run -p 8080:8080 rate0limiter

## Design 
1. Algo - Sliding Window - 1 Min Window
2. Thread Safety - ConcurrentHashMap and ConcurrentLinkedDeque
3. Extensibility - Strategy Pattern for swapping also - like fixed window, leaky bucket
